| Field    | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| SSN      | int         | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| emp_id   | int         | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| city     | varchar(20) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| dob      | date        | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| adhar_no | int         | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+

